{"tid":2119165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大灣區內地事業單位招聘港澳居民　應擁護共產黨領導","createTime":"2020-07-22T03:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T03:25:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e0eac6f7fa438d4dfd2899db177b75138bc02e8","tid":2119165,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1539176_1_20200722103515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1539176_1_20200722103515.jpg&h=dff0a92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東省人社廳公布，粵港澳大灣區內地事業單位招聘港澳居民的《管理辦法》。根據《管理辦法》，合資格的港澳居民可以參加廣州、深圳、珠海等9個城市事業單位的公開招聘。<br />\n<br />\n港澳居民指兩地永久居民中沒有外國居留權的中國公民，應聘者應該擁護中國共產黨領導和社會主義制度，維護祖國的統一、安全、榮譽和利益等，應徵時需要提交《無犯罪紀錄》等文件。<br />\n<br />\n獲聘用的港澳居民將享受薪酬、養老保險、醫療保險等待遇，如果需要出國或者出境執行公務，需要將有關證件交由規定部門保管，如果因私事出國，需要執行國家和省的相關管理規定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539176-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539176-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB2Fzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=12eaea4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539176-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0cd1d986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539176-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"26de7b83b54d57cfa17f04651d59831aef4b31ba","tid":2119165,"uid":197640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0e0eac6f7fa438d4dfd2899db177b75138bc02e8","tid":2119165,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1539176_1_20200722103515.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1539176_1_20200722103515.jpg&h=dff0a92e&